data.description: This ranch style home offers comfortable and convenient living space.  Walk into a spacious living room with enough space for an office.  Adjacent to the living room is the spacious kitchen which incudes a convenient breakfast bar perfect for enjoying quick meals with a view  into the dining room.  A pantry is available to store groceries and kitchen supplies.  The home features 3 roomy bedrooms and 1 and 1/2 bathrooms.  You walk outside into a large gated yard with a 2.5 car garage and located close to a park.   Being sold As Is.   2022 taxes - $4,319.42 with Homeowners exemption.   Needs some repairs.  Seller will provide 1-year Home Warranty.
